        "client_msg_id": "3130f689-a16e-4863-baee-53a65209906d",
        "text": "From an IA perspective, this looks like filtering facets (that is, filtering your list of facets, not facets which perform filtering).  There are faceted navigation views on Amazon which do this, where if you navigate by category instead of by search, you get ever more complicated facets available to you (and then they all go away once you've picked enough).  Surely there's literature about structuring that?",
